01:26:00.614 --> 01:26:02.158
Idontfeelgood.

01:26:09.749 --> 01:26:12.626
[Children laughing]

01:26:26.057 --> 01:26:28.851
[Children laughing, chattering]

01:26:37.485 --> 01:26:38.736
[Cackling]

01:26:38.819 --> 01:26:42.281
