at every funeral.

01:27:00.216 --> 01:27:02.051
- I bet you are.
- [Chuckles]

01:27:02.134 --> 01:27:03.052
[Tires screech]

01:27:03.135 --> 01:27:04.762
[Child] You look so good!

01:27:05.888 --> 01:27:07.348
Happy Halloween.

01:27:07.431 --> 01:27:10.601
Oh, my! What beautiful children.

