01:27:44.468 --> 01:27:45.594
Herman?

01:27:46.846 --> 01:27:49.140
I know. It's perfect.

01:27:49.223 --> 01:27:52.977
It's more than perfect, it's breathtaking.

01:27:54.103 --> 01:27:57.857
