01:28:26.385 --> 01:28:28.095
Yeah, you're the man of the house.

01:28:29.388 --> 01:28:32.016
Look, Barbara.

01:28:36.270 --> 01:28:41.317
I must inform you
that we munsters were not born yesterday.

01:28:41.942 --> 01:28:45.946
